node.text: Thank you everyone who tuned in sorry for  the technological difficulties. Follow Ben & Jerry’s campaign to #EndQualifiedImmunity here: @campaigntoendqi

node.text: 🙏🏾♥️I want to take a moment and thank God for My daughters continued healing after having her tonsils & adenoids removed. This is such a hard recover for a new parents  to watch but I remain calm in trusting God. Lil Pj is so strong and she has been able to weather the ups and downs of this recovery like a lil champ.  I can’t help but want to also pray for the many other parents of children who were at her hospital I pray Gods angels continue to watch over those babies and that they have a full recovery! Thank you to all family and friends who have text and sent flowers. I love you and it is much appreciated! Pj is still kinda in the thick of it after a week in hospital but she’s doing much,much better. If you have been through this surgery before you know toddlers can be a lil stubborn but with love and encouragement they make it through. Love you lil pooh bear @pilarjhena
